---
import CaseStudyLayout from '../../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro';
---

<CaseStudyLayout org="Discovery" role="UX Designer" year="2013–2015">

  <section>
    <span class="cs-section-label animate">Context</span>
    <h2 class="cs-section-title animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">A portfolio of brands without a shared design language</h2>
    <p class="animate" style="--delay: 0.15s">Discovery operated a portfolio of streaming brands and connected device experiences, each evolving independently. There was no shared design system; each product team made its own component decisions, leading to inconsistent user experiences, duplicated engineering effort, and a growing maintenance burden as the device landscape expanded.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <span class="cs-section-label animate">My Scope</span>
    <div class="cs-scope-grid">
      <div class="cs-scope-item animate">
        <span class="cs-scope-label">Team</span>
        <span class="cs-scope-value">Design systems team supporting multiple brand product teams</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-scope-item animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">
        <span class="cs-scope-label">Reporting</span>
        <span class="cs-scope-value">UX Designer within central design organization</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-scope-item animate" style="--delay: 0.15s">
        <span class="cs-scope-label">Org Placement</span>
        <span class="cs-scope-value">Platform team serving Discovery's streaming portfolio</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-scope-item animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">
        <span class="cs-scope-label">Influence</span>
        <span class="cs-scope-value">Cross-brand; defining shared patterns adopted across multiple streaming products and device types</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <span class="cs-section-label animate">Strategic Challenge</span>
    <h2 class="cs-section-title animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">Scaling consistency without killing brand identity</h2>
    <p class="animate" style="--delay: 0.15s">The challenge wasn't just creating a component library; it was building a system flexible enough to serve distinct brand identities while enforcing the structural consistency needed to ship efficiently across platforms. Each brand team had its own priorities and timelines, and any shared system needed to reduce their workload, not add governance overhead.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <span class="cs-section-label animate">Strategic Moves</span>
    <ul>
      <li class="animate">Designed a cross-platform design system with a theming architecture that separated brand expression from structural patterns; enabling consistency without homogenization</li>
      <li class="animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">Defined component specifications for connected TV, mobile, and web with device-appropriate interaction models sharing a common foundation</li>
      <li class="animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">Worked with engineering to establish a shared component implementation strategy that reduced duplication and accelerated delivery across brand teams</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <span class="cs-section-label animate">Impact</span>
    <div class="cs-metrics">
      <div class="cs-metric animate">
        <span class="cs-metric-value">Multiple</span>
        <span class="cs-metric-label">Streaming brands unified under one system</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-metric animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">
        <span class="cs-metric-value">3+</span>
        <span class="cs-metric-label">Device platforms supported</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="animate" style="--delay: 0.15s">The design system became the shared foundation for Discovery's streaming experiences, reducing time-to-ship for new features and enabling brand teams to focus on differentiation rather than re-solving structural problems.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <span class="cs-section-label animate">Selected Visual Evidence</span>
    <div class="cs-visuals animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">
      <div class="cs-visual">
        <img src="/images/projects/discovery-tile.jpg" alt="Discovery design system" />
        <span class="cs-visual-caption">Cross-platform design system supporting Discovery's portfolio of streaming brands</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</CaseStudyLayout>
